## Task 3: Run a DNS Lookup on a Known Domain

dig scanme.nmap.org
#Using dig tool to query a test domain provided by Nmap. Passive recon tool without touching the target

; <<>> DiG 9.20.9-1-Debian <<>> scanme.nmap.org
